      "title": "An explosion in a mosque in Afghanistan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Al Jazeera reported that 21 people were killed and 21 others were injured in an explosion that occurred today (02) during a prayer in a mosque in the city of Herat, Afghanistan.",
        "This bomb attack has been aimed at Mujib Ansari, who is a member of the main ranks of the Taliban organization. It is suspected that IS terrorists have carried out the attack."
      ],
